title: Harper's Burger Bar
typeOfFood: American, Organic, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Canadian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Casual restaurant and bar. Build your own burger with a chickpea patty, with buns or lettuce, or get the veggie stack, veggie hot dog, or vegan sandwich. Also has a quinoa and sprouted rice salad among other veggie choices. Uses some biodegradable packaging materials.
